text: Elizabeth "Betsy" Russell (born September 6, 1963) is an American actress. She is known for playing Jill Tuck in the Saw movie series from 2006 to 2010. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:American stage actors Category:American video game actors Category:Actors from San Diego Category:Movie producers from California Category:Actors from Santa Monica, California
